---
title: Maple-Ginger Chicken Breasts Stir-Fry with Garlic Rice
description: Maple, ginger and soy sauce team up to make a zippy sauce that will make this stir-fry night a memorable one. In this sweet and savoury sauce, you'll find carrots, peppers and juicy chicken.  A base of garlicky rice and a garnish of green onions complete this stir-fry sensation.
